      },
      {
        "text": "In the coders channel, Fixer posted the same communication support job opportunity for their international developer team. A user named Diwash Budhathoki shared a QR code image along with a network address string. Issa, a digital artist, introduced themselves and offered services including digital art, animations, and banners, asking if the team or any community members were in need of an artist or co-artist and offering to provide samples upon request.",
